    "attributes": {
        "action": "Legislate to ban participants wearing face coverings at demonstrations",
        "additional_details": "Introduce legislation that would result in the arrest of any attendee of a demonstration/protest wearing face covering (ie a mask/balaclava) and removal from the scene.",
        "background": "Government should introduce legislation to make it an offence to attend a demonstration or counter-demonstration wearing face coverings. All participants should be showing their faces, or, be arrested so that they can be identified.",
